metadata.name: Areia
metadata.description:
The sunlight soaking into skin, the breeze is caressing body. There are few feelings as reassuring as the sensation of sand between your toes and fingers, your hips, back, your breast and neck.

''Never stop believing in YOUR dreams. Have courage to live the life YOU want. Work hard, accept challenges and build YOUR castles...one by one...''

Size: 7000 x 6400
